<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="pt" data-theme="light"><head><%- include('partials-head', { title: 'MatemaLab | Login admin' }) %></head><body><main class="login-shell"><section class="login-card"><a href="/" class="brand" aria-label="Voltar à página inicial"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 48 L22 16 L32 39 L42 22 L54 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><circle cx="32" cy="39" r="5" fill="currentColor"></circle></svg><span>MatemaLab</span></a><div><p class="eyebrow">Área reservada</p><h1>Entrar no painel de publicação</h1><p>Os alunos não precisam de conta. Só tu tens acesso a esta área para publicar ou apagar exercícios.</p></div><% if (flash) { %><div class="flash <%= flash.type %>"><%= flash.message %></div><% } %><form method="post" action="/admin/login" class="auth-form"><label><span>Utilizador</span><input type="text" name="username" placeholder="admin" required></label><label><span>Password</span><input type="password" name="password" placeholder="A tua password" required></label><button class="btn btn-primary full-width" type="submit">Entrar</button></form></section></main><script src="/app.js" defer></script></body></html>